  "stem": "<p>A right triangle has legs with lengths of <math><mn>24</mn></math> centimeters and <math><mn>12</mn></math> centimeters. What is the length of this triangle's hypotenuse, in centimeters?</p>",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
      "content": "<p><math><mn>12</mn><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt></math></p>"
