  ],
  "rationale": "<p>Choice A is correct. By the Pythagorean theorem, hypotenuse = \u221a(24\u00b2 + 12\u00b2) = \u221a(576 + 144) = \u221a720 = \u221a(144\u00b75) = 12\u221a5.</p><p>Choice B mis-simplifies the radical. Choice C adds the legs. Choice D is 24\u00b2 + 12\u00b2 without taking the square root.</p>",
